         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Education Office, ¶ Dunedin ¶   ¶ 14th. March  ¶ 188 ¶ 9. ¶ My Dear Sir Ferdinand, ¶  ¶ I send you on a few specimens of an Atriplex that has long puzzled me very much. Will you kindly let me know as ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">89.03.14a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Donald Petrie</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name> buchananii</seg> (MEL 2352095). Annotated by M: 'Answ 22/3/89'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Education Office,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">Dunedin</seg>
               <seg>
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>14th. March <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">188</seg>9.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My Dear Sir Ferdinand,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I send you on a few specimens of an <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name> that has long puzzled me very much. Will you kindly let me know as soon as you can if it is known to you, and also say what you think about the <name key="Glossostigma">Glossostigma</name> I sent a few weeks ago. The <name key="Atriplex">Atriplex</name> if native is of course quite new to New Zealand. It grows plentifully in the dry and bare parts of the plains in the interior of Otago. As it is spreading I have suspicions that it may be introduced, but it was a common plant even twenty years ago in the places where it now grows It is only the other day that I observed the female flowers though I have known the plant for years, and supposed it to be <name key="Chenopodium%20pusillum">Chenopodium pusillum</name>, Hook. f. This was the reason why I never examined it more carefully before. Pray do me the favour of giving your opinions about these two plants. Could you spare me a copy of your recent work on the plants of Victoria?<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B88.11.02?</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With best wishes</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours very sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>D. Petrie.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir F. Von Mueller,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
